Description: Finite candidate-set approximate optimal designs for group testing
    and related experiments, using convex optimization (CVXR) and equivalence
    checks. Builds on the regression / Fisher-information formulation: supply
    candidate pool layouts (or other labels) and a map into regression vectors
    (e.g. score or square-root information contributions). Helpers are included
    for a homogeneous prevalence model with perfect assays.
